name: The Killer Cat - Part 11
description: I went to the Deep Web, in a place that only exists in virtual reality, and there I found a group of very dark cats. They were Sorry's stray children, called "The Lost Litter". They told me I would have to pay 2 ethereum for the rat-killing job. I felt sorry for the little brats, but laser, bro, laser! When I saw it, Germs' cat, my friend, was selected for the job. He came in my lap calmly, but when he got home, he terrified the rats! And maybe me too, a little bit.
